### Test Firebase Token Verification - Invalid Token Case
POST http://localhost:8000/verify-token
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token

### Variables
@firebase_token = your_firebase_token_here

# Note: Replace 'your_firebase_token_here' with a valid Firebase ID token
# To get a valid token:
# 1. Sign in to your Firebase application
# 2. Get the ID token from the authenticated user
# 3. Copy and paste it as the value for @firebase_token